{"tid":2376094,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"網媒《娛賓》女記者否認在女廁內拒捕　案件4.13開審","createTime":"2021-01-22T13:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T16:49:19.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0a0c9078c0fc1a2ba846317792f7ee0f8958ae83","tid":2376094,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T13:36:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/5020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_info%2F5020&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5F3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=446262ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/5020</a><br />\n<br />\n《娛賓》女記者籲當日在場人士提供資料  KY：「香港發生太多不公平事，已作最壞打算」<br />\n<br />\n【娛賓】《娛賓》女記者何家欣（KY）被控「抗拒警務人員罪」，今午再於九龍城裁判法院答辯，被告人不認罪。裁判官將案件押後至本年4月13日上午0930九龍城裁判法院再訊。<br />\n<br />\n何其後向記者表示心情很緊張及擔心 ，她指現時香港發生很多不公平事，已作最壞打算會被判罪。但自己會保持希望及觀望態度去面對，更笑言「如果要坐監，希望同周庭一齊坐。」。其後亦呼籲任何人於上年5月10至11日於洗衣街花園目睹事件經過或有資料提供，可向《娛賓》提供資料。（全文 (<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/109934763988991/posts/260246792291120/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F109934763988991%2Fposts%2F260246792291120%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5F3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=deac79c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/109934763988991/posts/260246792291120/?d=n</a>)）<br />\n<br />\n📌 【搜證部】《娛賓》尋人/尋片 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_evidence/265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_evidence%2F265&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5F3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=c74a7fe3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_evidence/265</a>)<br />\n<br />\n#20210122新聞"},{"pid":"3b6b18a7f6e2bc3d3488be526dec951665dfeb82","tid":2376094,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T13:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src